<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Jul1934"><font color="red">28 July 1934</font> <i>Selected Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): If any notice of my fragment appeared in the English press in which Lucia&apos;s name is mentioned will you please send it to me. The Dutch firm was willing to do the Chaucer poem without any money from my side. We came here a day or so ago to allow &hellip; workmen time to get in order &hellip; a flat &hellip; Did L&eacute;on send you a bundle of MS? &hellip; I have been working very hard and hope to get on quickly once I am in dock again. </div>
